Ask HN: Do you use a bookmark manager?
text: As my browser bookmark folders get more and more messy I feel the need to migrate to a different solution. I'm looking for the ability to add brief comments/notes/tags to the links I save, to record metadata such as: where I found the link, what I thought about it and what it might be useful for.
